---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Info — Explicit Studio" description="Explicit Studio is a full cycle creative studio led by Srijan Mahajan, creating monopolising brands for technology startups.">

  <!-- Studio Philosophy -->
  <section class="info-philosophy reveal">
    <h1 class="info-philosophy__headline">Look hard enough & there's an interesting story everywhere. Including B2B SaaS.</h1>
    <div class="info-philosophy__body">
      <p>But somewhere along the way, tech startups developed a brand problem. Everyone talks about narratives and taste, but everything still looks the same. The same templates. The same interchangeable positioning. The same "AI-powered" tagline.</p>
      <p>We believe tech startups will become the consumer brands of tomorrow. Which means they can't just be functional anymore. They have to mean something. They have to make people feel something.</p>
      <p>Explicit exists at the intersection of art & technology to help startups build brands that people remember, trust, and talk about.</p>
      <p>You've made something the world needs. <strong>Make it Explicit.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- We Believe -->
  <section class="info-beliefs reveal">
    <h2 class="info-beliefs__title">We Believe</h2>
    <div class="info-beliefs__list">
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>Tech is culture.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>The story is part of the product.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>A good brand is a business advantage.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="info-beliefs__item">
        <h3>Startups die when they stop taking creative risk.</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Srijan -->
  <section class="info-about reveal">
    <div class="info-about__grid">
      <div class="info-about__body">
        <p>I'm Srijan. I've spent my life thinking about what makes people pay attention & build trust.</p>
        <p>I started playing drums at 15, became the drummer for Parikrama, played with Shubha Mudgal, opened for Iron Maiden, and performed at The Kennedy Centre — 1000+ concerts across the world. Then I spent years in film and advertising learning how stories work, what makes them stick, and what makes them forgettable.</p>
        <p>Then I started building startups. I built Pause, a mental health platform that broke its category with its positioning, and Attis, India's first biohacking & longevity community. Building those taught me what agencies will never understand — what it actually feels like to be a founder. That's why I built Explicit.</p>
        <p>You can learn more about me on my <a href="https://srijanmahajan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">website</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-about__portrait">
        <img src="/images/srijan-portrait.JPG" alt="Srijan Mahajan" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="info-services reveal">
    <div class="info-services__inner">
      <h2 class="info-services__title">How We Work</h2>
      <div class="info-services__intro">
        <p>Explicit doesn't have account managers, elaborate processes, or bloated teams. You talk to me & a handpicked team of designers, developers, copywriters, motion artists, and strategists. We understand your startup, we move fast, and we build things that work. No scope creep, no surprise invoices, no design-by-committee.</p>
        <p><strong>We work with a maximum of 3 clients per quarter.</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-services__offers">
        <div class="info-services__offer">
          <h3>Brand Sprint — 6 Weeks</h3>
          <p class="info-services__offer-sub">Everything you need to go from unknown to unforgettable.</p>
          <p class="info-services__offer-label">What you walk away with:</p>
          <div class="info-services__deliverables">
            <p>&rarr; Brand positioning document</p>
            <p>&rarr; Complete narrative & messaging framework</p>
            <p>&rarr; Brand identity & visual system</p>
            <p>&rarr; Designed and developed website</p>
            <p>&rarr; 90-day content strategy</p>
            <p>&rarr; Brand guidelines</p>
            <p>&rarr; 30 days of post-launch support</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-services__offer">
          <h3>Monthly Partnership — Ongoing</h3>
          <p class="info-services__offer-sub">An ongoing creative partner for the work that comes after launch.</p>
          <div class="info-services__deliverables">
            <p>&rarr; GTM strategy and campaign architecture</p>
            <p>&rarr; Advertising creatives and copy</p>
            <p>&rarr; Campaign concepts and execution</p>
            <p>&rarr; Content strategy and production</p>
            <p>&rarr; Weekly syncs — no ticket systems, no queues</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-services__offer">
          <h3>1:1 with Srijan — 60 Minutes</h3>
          <p class="info-services__offer-sub">Not ready for a full engagement? Book a 1:1 session with Srijan to work through anything — brand positioning, go-to-market strategy, growth challenges, content direction, or whatever's keeping you up at night. One hour, no fluff, just direct answers.</p>
          <p class="info-services__offer-price">$1,000 / session</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary info-services__offer-cta">Get in touch <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="info-faq reveal">
    <div class="info-faq__list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What kind of startups do you work with?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Ambitious ones. We work with founders in AI, Crypto, Healthcare & D2C. If you believe brand is a business advantage and you're not looking for safe work, we should talk.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          How much does it cost?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>It depends on the scope. Get in touch and we'll figure out if there's a fit before talking numbers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What's your process?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We start with strategy — understanding your market, competition, and unfair advantages. Then we build the brand, website & content. The Brand Sprint is 6 weeks end-to-end. Monthly partnerships are ongoing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Do you do just websites? Just logos?
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>No. We work best when we build the full brand — from positioning to identity to website to content. That's how the best work happens.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Philosophy ===== */
  .info-philosophy {
    padding: 40px var(--section-padding-x) var(--section-padding-y);
  }

  .info-philosophy__headline {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .info-philosophy__body {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .info-philosophy__body p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-philosophy__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-philosophy__body strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ===== We Believe ===== */
  .info-beliefs {
    padding: 0 var(--section-padding-x) var(--section-padding-y);
  }

  .info-beliefs__title {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .info-beliefs__list {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .info-beliefs__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 24px 0;
  }

  .info-beliefs__item h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ===== About Srijan ===== */
  .info-about {
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
  }

  .info-about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .info-about__body p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-about__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-about__body a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .info-about__body a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .info-about__portrait {
    position: sticky;
    top: 40px;
  }

  .info-about__portrait img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  /* ===== How We Work ===== */
  .info-services {
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
  }

  .info-services__title {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .info-services__inner {
    max-width: none;
  }

  .info-services__intro {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .info-services__intro p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .info-services__intro p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-services__intro strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .info-services__offers {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .info-services__offer {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px);
  }

  .info-services__offer h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .info-services__offer-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .info-services__offer-label {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .info-services__deliverables p {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .info-services__offer-price {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .info-services__offer-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
  }

  /* ===== FAQ ===== */
  .info-faq {
    padding: 0 var(--section-padding-x) var(--section-padding-y);
  }

  .info-faq__list {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .faq-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-answer {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .info-cta {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) var(--section-padding-x);
  }

  .info-cta__inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .info-cta__inner h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .info-cta__button {
    padding: 16px 40px;
  }

  .info-cta__email {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .info-cta__email:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .info-about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .info-about__portrait {
      position: static;
      order: -1;
    }

    .info-services__offer {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .info-beliefs__item h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-h3);
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // FAQ accordion
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach((btn) => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      btn.closest('.faq-item')?.classList.toggle('open');
    });
  });

  // Scroll reveal
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.1 }
  );

  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach((el) => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
